text: José Luis Aguilera Rico (born 17 February 1979) is a Mexican politician from the Citizens' Movement. From 2006 to 2009 he served as Deputy of the LX Legislature of the Mexican Congress representing Querétaro. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Querétaro Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:Citizens' Movement (Mexico) politicians Category:21st-century Mexican politicians Category:Mexican lawyers Category:Members of the Congress of Querétaro
